1 hour ago, Foxy5410 said:

Why does this github page not exists anymore?

Starcrusher took it down for the summer so that he could make it work with his new mod Kerbal Star Systems 2. Expect GU to return in a few weeks.

For some reason when the ocean is in frame on Narath i get very low frames and i have no idea how to fix that. This is the second planet i visit and its also buggy. Also the planet looks weird when going between scaledspace and close in model. I get the impression this modpack isnt well made. Also the science messages dont see that i turned on habbitable mode on Narath. Are there even different ones at all?
